CleanIndia

Project Goals:

Main aim of this project is to implement swatchbharat scheme digitally by providing kiosks which includes an application to guide users.

Project Approach:

This project is mainly based on java ,we make use of oracle database where we store details of user(Firstname,lastname,emailid,password,mobile number)
In database we make use of important concept called JOINS to generate coupons.After giving recycle wasteage details we have to generate coupons
to individual user.Hence, these joins are used to join every single user to the coupons he/she gets after they submitting their recycle details and 
eventually sending updated coupons to registered mobile numbers of users.

